item.description:
Paws in the Park, presented by Massage Envy of Evergreen Run, South Windsor and the South Windsor Jaycees

5/2 10-3 Rotary Pavilion Nevers Park South Windsor

A free all day dog event featuring contests, attraction, demonstrations, dog walk, vendors, food, tea cup auction and more. Celebrity judges include Wendy Steele, Jeannine Jersey and Ryan Hanrahan. Prizes for all our participants compliments of Petco. Great for the kids as the event includes a free moon bounce and coloring contest. Proceed benefit the Fidelco Guide Dog Foundation and South Windsor Bark Park

Visit www.swjaycees.org for more details
